

Middle Market Investment Partners | Hancock Capital Management



















Investment Partners for the Middle Market
Hancock Capital Management's private-market solutions consist of equity investments, senior and junior debt financing in sponsored and unsponsored transactions, and primary and secondary private equity fund investments. We manage these investments on a coordinated basis and with a common focus on the U.S. middle market.






