Shortly about us Mezzanine financing is a flexible form of capital that can help your business or real estate project not only to develop, but also to go through all sorts of transitions. However, it does require hard work to arrange it. We are not brokers or financial advisers, but we have worked on getting mezzanine capital for our own company. This site reflects what we've learned since that time.
